            You require {under} units of {inventory.material} to reach your desired level.
        |elif under = 1:
            You require 1 unit of {inventory.material} to reach your desired level.
        }
    |elif inventory.desired:
        You are above your desired level for {inventory.material}.
    |elif inventory.minimum :
